**Nightmare Team**
Nightmare team wins when all players are either dead, unaligned, sleepless or part of the Nightmare team. All members of the team know each other.

__Roles:__
<?Reaper:> *Reaper*
<?Wraith:> *Wraith*
<?Spirit:> *Spirit (T)*

__Formalized__
Win Condition: `@(Attribute:Sleepless)`
Inherit: `Sleepless`
Starting: Join `Nightmare`
